                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d254">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00/3–3149: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul General at Peiping</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Clubb</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peiping</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-03-31T15:00:00+08:00"
                            >March 31, 1949—3 p. m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received March 31—4:26 a. m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>526. ReContel 525, March 31. Recommend categorical firm denial allegation New
                    China Agency despite fact identification bombers as American flag B–29 type
                    ambiguous.</p>
                <p>Repeated Nanking and Shanghai.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Clubb</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
